# Williamsburg (Lexington Themes) — global

- **Publisher:** Lexington Themes; human-facing links and support URLs follow the pattern in the root `README.md` (documentation, changelog, support — do not invent new domains).
- **Package scope:** This repo is the **`@lexington/williamsburg`** Astro theme only; do not claim dependencies that are not in `package.json`.
- **Imports:** Use the project alias `@/` → `src/` (see `tsconfig.json`). Prefer existing components over new duplicative UI.
- **Design system folder:** The UI primitives live under `src/components/fundations/` (intentional spelling **fundations** — do not rename or “fix” to foundations).
- **Layouts:** `BaseLayout` wraps most pages; domain layouts include `BlogLayout`, `StoreLayout`, `HelpcenterLayout`, `LegalLayout`. Respect their `frontmatter` prop contracts when touching pages.
- **Change style:** Keep diffs small and consistent with existing patterns (e.g. `Wrapper`, `Text`, `Button` from fundations). Avoid drive-by refactors and unrelated files.
